{"tid":2167335,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"基層近半工時減 逾60%焦慮","createTime":"2020-08-21T04:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T04:58:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7d556338fcb7394950863d0eea3a2d1ef947a8db","tid":2167335,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/EHVBSUAFSBAHRE27KTF6EW4SRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FEHVBSUAFSBAHRE27KTF6EW4SRI%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=cda24338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FEHVBSUAFSBAHRE27KTF6EW4SRI%2F&h=017ae6e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/EHVBSUAFSBAHRE27KTF6EW4SRI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n基層近半工時減 逾60%焦慮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jgjVka8x1z_Tyvg7ENufhanXTi4=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LY2F43HMWNBNJENRTFKDCQNNH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjgjVka8x1z_Tyvg7ENufhanXTi4%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLY2F43HMWNBNJENRTFKDCQNNH4.jpg&h=1b708782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■關注綜援低收入聯盟調查發現，油尖旺收入低於10,000元的居民中，近半工作時數減少。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武肺疫情持續，統計處早前公佈，5至7月的失業率為6.1%。關注綜援低收入聯盟於上月19日至本月6日訪問215名油尖旺居民，近半受訪者表示工作時數減少，逾六成受訪者因失業問題處於中度焦慮狀態，須到精神科求診，有失業人士更現自殺傾向。<br />\n<br />\n關注綜援低收入聯盟上月19日至本月6日訪問了215名油尖旺居民，介乎25至64歲，當中61.3%人收入低於$10,000，近半人表示工作時數減少，更有25%人失業。<br />\n<br />\n其中，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n團體按照焦慮自我評估量表（GAD-7）調查受訪者焦慮狀態。結果顯示超過62%人每日處於焦慮狀態，66%人。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逾八成長者因疫情低落<br />\n<br />\n另有調查發現，疫情下逾八成長者社交生活受影響，亦有起過五成長者因疫情令情緒變得負面，出現擔心、驚慌、困擾等狀況。有。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n明愛安老服務高級督導主任崔允然指，現時大多社福機構已開展網上活動，。。。。。。。。。"}]}